        </p>
        <p>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;员工类别&nbsp;
            <select class="easyui-combobox" id="employerTypeDetail" style="width:145px;">
                <option value="1" selected="true">试用期员工</option>
                <option value="2">实习期员工</option>
                <option value="3">临时雇员</option>
                <option value="0">正式员工</option>
            </select>
